cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the development of models for computing continuous word representations. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with improving the accuracy of semantic similarity. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural network-inspired models.
